data.description: Newly remodeled home in TOWNE PARK community! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home has been completely renovated with modern amenities. Newly painted exterior. New laminate flooring throughout. Newer roof 2 years old AC is 6 years old. The spacious living room features volume ceilings and large windows that let in plenty of natural light. The updated kitchen boasts granite countertops, backsplash, stainless steel appliances, plenty of cabinet space, and a center island. The open concept living and dining areas are perfect for entertaining, with plenty of space for guests to gather. The bedrooms are all generously sized, with plenty of closet space and the bathrooms have been beautifully updated with new vanities, fixtures, and tile work. 2 Car garage fenced yard for privacy. The backyard is a private oasis, with a large, covered lanai, great for entertaining, and the backyard has a creek view and private bridge that extends over the creek quick gate access to elementary school.  Have a glass of wine or coffee on your private bridge while enjoying the nature view.  The backyard has so much potential to turn it into your outdoor living space.  Also 2 Charter schools in the area Hillsborough Academic Math & Science and Horizon Charter School. Located just minutes from shopping Citrus Park Mall, International Mall, Dining, and Entertainment, AMC Theater's, Tampa International Airport, Beaches, Hospitals, Upper Tampa Bay Bike Trail,  this home offers both comfort and convenience. No Flood Insurance required!
